text: Jordan Boy (born 20 March 1994) is a French footballer who currently plays for Championnat de France Amateur 2 side Louhans-Cuiseaux. He plays as a midfielder. == Club career == Boy is a youth exponent from Evian Thonon Gaillard. He made his Ligue 1 debut on 23 May 2015 against SM Caen.
